@startuml
title State diagram for the Staff Member class

[*] --> Unassigned : Assign to Client or Campaign

state "Unassigned" as Unassigned
state "Assigned to Client" as AssignedToClient
state "Assigned to Campaign" as AssignedToCampaign
state "Working" as Working
state "Unemployed" as Unemployed
state "Archived" as Archived

Unassigned --> AssignedToClient : Assign to Client
Unassigned --> AssignedToCampaign : Assign to Campaign
AssignedToClient --> Working
AssignedToCampaign --> Working
Working --> Unassigned : Remove Assignment
Working --> Unemployed : Leave Job
Unemployed --> Archived : After some time has passed
Archived --> [*]
@enduml
